data.description: "A Nice 3-Bedroom Home in Coveted Naples Area with Spacious Backyard!"  One of the standout features of this home has to be the large and lushly landscaped backyard. Providing ample play space for kids or pets, it’s also the perfect retreat for alfresco dining or simply unwinding under the Florida sun. You will appreciate the attached garage with space for one vehicle, as well as additional room for storage. An over sized patio open to Huge backyard with fruit trees, fenced throughout, directly on the canal. As an added bonus, the property also features a versatile guest room that can serve as a home office, game room, or additional sleeping quarters for visiting family or friends.
